    "title": "European Heritage Label: 2027 selection procedure now open",
    "link": "https://culture.ec.europa.eu/whats-new/news/european-heritage-label-2027-selection-procedure-now-open",
    "pubDate": "2026-04-09T13:06:42.000Z",
    "content": "<html><head></head><body><h1 class=\"title-h1 eac-page-title\">European Heritage Label: 2027 selection procedure now open</h1>\n<span><span>csudaga</span></span>\n<span><time datetime=\"2026-04-09T15:06:42+02:00\" title=\"Thursday, April 9, 2026 - 15:06\">Thu, 04/09/2026 - 15:06</time>\n</span>\n<div class=\"ecl\"><p>The selection procedure for the 2027 edition of the European Heritage Label (EHL) action is open. Interested organisations should contact the EHL coordinators in their respective countries for the details of the application, as this first stage of the process is done at national level.</p></div>\n<div class=\"ecl-u-type-bold ecl-u-mb-m\">Intro Text</div><div class=\"eac-hero\"><p>Heritage organisations are invited to apply for the call. The initial procedure is carried out at national level.</p></div>\n  <div>\n    <div>Card image</div>\n              <div>\n\n</div>\n          </div>\n                <div id=\"paragraph-6349\" class=\"stripe-basic-link--items\">\n                                                           </div></body></html>",
