    "title": "Dig into Creative Europe’s achievements through stats and data visualisations",
    "link": "https://culture.ec.europa.eu/whats-new/news/dig-into-creative-europes-achievements-through-stats-and-data-visualisations",
    "pubDate": "2026-04-08T10:46:54.000Z",
    "content": "<html><head></head><body><h1 class=\"title-h1 eac-page-title\">Dig into Creative Europe’s achievements through stats and data visualisations</h1>\n<span><span>csudaga</span></span>\n<span><time datetime=\"2026-04-08T12:46:54+02:00\" title=\"Wednesday, April 8, 2026 - 12:46\">Wed, 04/08/2026 - 12:46</time>\n</span>\n<div class=\"ecl\"><p>How many projects has Creative Europe supported in past years? In which cultural and creative sectors were they active? How many grantees has Culture Moves Europe supported in recent years? Where do grantees travel to and from, around Europe and beyond?</p><h2>Up-to-date, interactive data on Creative Europe</h2><p>These data and more are now available in interactive overview, providing access to the programme's performance metrics and data to anyone interested. The accompanying page <a href=\"https://culture.ec.europa.eu/resources/creative-europe-in-numbers?\">“Creative Europe in numbers”</a> guides you through the dashboard and offers ready-made dynamic charts to get you initiated into the wealth of the programme data.</p><p>With this tool the European Commission aims to foster transparency and deepen the understanding about Creative Europe's activities and accomplishments through data </p></div></body></html>",
